                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Sheṭar</title>
                            
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">שטר</title>
                            
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Acknowledgment of the obligation of the Jewish community of
                                    Northampton to pay an annual rent of half a mark to the Priory
                                    of St Andrew, Northampton, for the burial ground outside the
                                    north gate of the town. Jewish witnesses are: Samuel Hazan ben
                                    Aaron, Benet ben Isaac, Samson ben Samson. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Latin and
                                    Hebrew duplicate of a lost charter of Samuel ben Aaron, Benet
                                    ben Isaac and Sampson ben Sampson acting on behalf of the Jewish
                                    community of Northampton.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                        
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                    
               
               
               
